{"word":"G4901 - συνεπιμαρτυρέω - synepimartyréō - soon-ep-ee-mar-too-reh'-o - Also bear witness","slug":"G4901","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνεπιμαρτυρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>synepimartyréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soon-ep-ee-mar-too-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Also bear witness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03C4;&#x03C5;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - sunepimartureo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soon-ep-ee-mar-too-reh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G1957\">G1957</a>; to <i>testify further jointly</i>, that is, <i>unite in adding evidence:</i> - also bear witness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1263\">G1263</a>, <a href=\"#/G1957\">G1957</a>, <a href=\"#/G2649\">G2649</a>, <a href=\"#/G3140\">G3140</a>, <a href=\"#/G3141\">G3141</a>, <a href=\"#/G3142\">G3142</a>, <a href=\"#/G3143\">G3143</a>, <a href=\"#/G3144\">G3144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4303\">G4303</a>, <a href=\"#/G4828\">G4828</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577\">G5577</a>"}]}